description:
On this week's episode of ANN International: ADRA captivates the European Parliament with a postcard campaign for child education. Also, a documentary about the "I Will Go Amazon Experience" inspires new missionaries.

In addition, AdventHealth renews sponsorship in races at Daytona Speedway. 

Stay tuned as ANN brings everything you have to know about what is happening in the church around the world. For a deeper dive into these headlines, visit https://www.adventist.news.
